### Required libraries to run this code:

*lsm303 sensor library:* https://github.com/pololu/lsm303-arduino/tree/master/LSM303

*adafruit nokia 5110 lcd library:* https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-PCD8544-Nokia-5110-LCD-library

*adafruit GFX library:* https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-GFX-Library

download .zip file then open arduino IDE and select sketch menu > include library > add .ZIP library.